title: In your own understanding, what is unpacking? - Quora

response.answer_text: To unpack is the remove your belongings from your luggage and put them away when you either arrive at or return from your destination. It is also to break an idea or open up a compressed computer program into its component parts.
In my own understanding,unpacking is the process same as un boxing.products ready to feed in line station. To be used for production for example.
